languages.text: "Das heißt, dass meine Leute Schwächlinge sind, und das werde ich bald ändern. Ich für meinen Teil habe seit dem Tag meiner Geburt eine robuste Konstitution."
languages.original_text: "That means that my people are weaklings, and I shall change that soon. As for me, I have been of stout constitution since the day I was born."

traits.locale_text: "Das heißt, dass meine Leute Schwächlinge sind, und das werde ich bald ändern. Und ich bin von Geburt an immer bei bester Gesundheit."
traits.speaker: Quetza-al_Winterscale

languages.text: "Bu da halkımın iradesiz insanlardan oluştuğunu gösteriyor. Yakında bunu değiştireceğim. Bana gelirsek doğduğum günden beri dayanıklı bir bünyeye sahip olmuşumdur."
languages.original_text: "That means that my people are weaklings, and I shall change that soon. As for me, I have been of stout constitution since the day I was born."
